{"id":46,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":46,"title":"Chapter 43: Jesus Christ Appears to the Nephites","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 43","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 43"],["h1","Jesus Christ Appears to the Nephites"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p3"},"Many Nephites gathered at the temple in Bountiful. They were amazed at the great changes in the land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.1"},"3 Nephi 11:1"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p5"},"The people were talking about Jesus Christ and the sign of his death."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.2"},"3 Nephi 11:2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p7"},"While they were talking, they heard a quiet voice from heaven. It made their hearts burn."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.3"},"3 Nephi 11:3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p9"},"At first they did not understand the voice, but when it spoke the third time, they understood it."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.4-6"},"3 Nephi 11:4–6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p11"},"The voice was Heavenly Father’s. It introduced Jesus Christ and told the people to listen to him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.7"},"3 Nephi 11:7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p13"},"Jesus Christ came down from heaven and stood among the people. They were afraid to speak because they did not understand what was happening. They thought Jesus was an angel."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.8"},"3 Nephi 11:8"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p15"},"He told them he was Jesus Christ, the one the prophets had said would come."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.10"},"3 Nephi 11:10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p17"},"Jesus told the people to come and feel the marks in his side and in his hands and feet, where he had been nailed to the cross."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.14"},"3 Nephi 11:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p19"},"Jesus wanted the people to know that he was their God and that he had died for their sins."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.14"},"3 Nephi 11:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p21"},"One by one the people felt the marks in Jesus’ side, hands, and feet. The people knew he was the Savior."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.15"},"3 Nephi 11:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p23"},"Then the people praised Jesus and fell at his feet and worshiped him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.17"},"3 Nephi 11:17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p25"},"Jesus called Nephi and 11 other men to him. He gave them priesthood power and taught them the right way to baptize."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.18,21-26"},"3 Nephi 11:18, 21–26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.1"},"3 Nephi 12:1"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p27"},"He told the Nephites to believe in him, repent, and keep the commandments. If they did not, they could not enter his kingdom."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.19-20"},"3 Nephi 12:19–20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p29"},"He taught the Nephites how to pray to Heavenly Father. He also taught them about fasting and said they would be forgiven if they forgave one another."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.6-18"},"3 Nephi 13:6–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p31"},"After teaching the people many things, Jesus told them to go home and think and pray about what he had said."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.1-3"},"3 Nephi 17:1–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p33"},"The Nephites began to cry. They did not want Jesus to leave yet."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.5"},"3 Nephi 17:5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p35"},"Jesus loved the Nephites. He told them to bring the people who were sick or hurt to him so he could heal them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.7"},"3 Nephi 17:7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.f18"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_046_18.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p37"},"Jesus healed these people. Everyone bowed down and worshiped him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-43-jesus-christ-appears-to-the-nephites.p38"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.9-10"},"3 Nephi 17:9–10"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
